(Before It's News)
By Lisa Haven
Project Veritas’ James O’Keefe is at it again. In a shocking turn of events this alternative media giant has managed to obtain 200+ hours of leaked information from inside CNN—the network directly involved with Hillary Clinton and who paraded alternative media as fake news, all while bolstering fake news themselves. As the saying goes, “Suspicion always haunts the guilty mind” or, as children put it, “he who smelt it dealt it.”
In the video below I expose a few of the bombshells and corruption that have been leaked on CNN as well as the increased censorship on any media outlet who opposes their reign. Here’s the breaking report….
